The '''Bing Crosby International Classic''' was a [[golf]] tournament on the [[LPGA Tour]] from 1974 to 1975.<ref>[http://www.lpga.com/content/Chronology70-79.pdf LPGA Tournament Chronology 1970-1979] {{webarchive |url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100102105959/http://www.lpga.com/content/Chronology70-79.pdf |date=January 2, 2010 }}</ref> It was played at the San Isidro Country Club in [[Guadalajara]], [[Mexico]].

==Winners==
*1975 [[Sue Roberts]]
*1974 [[Jane Blalock]]

