The '''Dongeui Turtle Fighters football''' program represents [[Dong-eui University]] in [[college football]] as members of the [[Korea American Football Association]]. Founded in 1982, the Turtle Fighters have won the Korea Collegiate Champions five times. The Turtle Fighters won the [[Tiger Bowl (game)|Tiger Bowl]] three times in a in row in 2006, 2007, and 2008. [[Seong-il Baek]] has been the Turtle Fighters head coach since 2002 {{fact|date=October 2017}}.
