{{Infobox sport governing body |name = Iran Taekwondo Association |abbrev = |logo = |logosize = |sport = [[Taekwondo]] |category = |image = |caption = |jurisdiction = [[Iran]] |founded = |aff = [[World Taekwondo Federation]] |affdate = |region = |regionyear = |headquarters = |location = |president = |chairman = |chairperson = |chair = |chiefexec = |vicepresident = |director = |secretary = |coach = |womenscoach = |key staff = |operating income = |sponsor = |year closed = |replaced = |prevfounded = |url = http://www.irantkd.ir |countryflag = Iran }}
[[File:S.Ali.Haghshenas.jpg|thumb|right|'''Ali Haghshenas''']] '''Iran Taekwondo Association''' "I.T.A" (Persian: '''کانون تکواندوکاران ایران''') is the first N.G.O of [[Iran]]ian [[sport]] which started its activities with the official authority of Iran's [[Ministry of Interior (Iran)|Interior Ministry]] and [[Ministry of Justice (Iran)|Justice Ministry]] in 2001.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://irantkd.ir/Newspaper/1380/T/01.jpg|format=JPG|title=Newspaper photograph|publisher=Irantkd.ir|accessdate=4 January 2015}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2012/07/28/sports/olympics/nikpah-of-afghanistan-symbolizes-peaceful-olympic-combat.html?_r=0|title=Afghan Contender Is Symbol of Peaceful Olympic Combat|newspaper=[[The New York Times]]|accessdate=4 January 2015}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.tehrantimes.com/sports/120080-is-irans-tsunami-set-to-become-the-most-dominant-force-in-taekwondo-|title= Is Iran’s "Tsunami" Set to Become the Most Dominant Force in Taekwondo?|newspaper=[[Tehran Times]]|accessdate=4 January 2015}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.arirang.co.kr/News/News_View.asp?nseq=118883&category=2|title=Asia Heartbeat arirang|author=|work=Irans Taekwondo Rises to the Top|accessdate=4 January 2015}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.worldtaekwondofederation.net/news-news/item/1620-is-iran-s-tsunami-set-to-become-the-most-dominant-force-in-taekwondo/1620-is-iran-s-tsunami-set-to-become-the-most-dominant-force-in-taekwondo|title=Is Iran’s "Tsunami" Set to Become the Most Dominant Force in Taekwondo?|publisher=Worldtaekwondofederation.net|accessdate=4 January 2015}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UEX1JIQDdOo|title=Iran's Taekwondo Rises to the Top [Arirang Today]|work=YouTube|accessdate=4 January 2015}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://sports.espn.go.com/espn/wire?id=7053912|title=Olympic taekwondo ditches sport's traditions|work=ESPN.com|accessdate=4 January 2015}}</ref>
This [[organization]] has not only established the first [[Taekwondo]] [[school]]s in Iran,<ref>{{cite web|url=http://irantkd.ir/Dorehaye%20Fanni/Madrese_En.htm|title=Opening of Taekwondo School with the presence of senior responsibles of I.T.A - Babol 4/11/2002|publisher=Irantkd.ir|accessdate=4 January 2015}}</ref> but also trained many Taekwondo official [[Coach (sport)|coaches]] and referees.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://irantkd.ir/_En/Seminars_En.htm|title=Iran Taekwondo Association - Congresses & Technical terms|publisher=Irantkd.ir|accessdate=4 January 2015}}</ref>
It has held many [[competition]]s in different age groups, from infants to teenagers, youngsters and adults.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.irantkd.ir/_En/Match_En.htm|title=Iran Taekwondo Association - Championships|publisher=Irantkd.ir|accessdate=4 January 2015}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.farsnews.com/newstext.php?nn=8904070684|title=سمينار علمي تخصصي كانون تكواندوكاران ايران برگزار شد|publisher=Farsnews.com|accessdate=4 January 2015}}</ref>
[[Ali Haghshenas]] is the [[Entrepreneur|founder]] and [[chairman]] of this organization.
== Government oppositions == The Iran Physical Education Organization and Iran Taekwondo Governmental Federation are two organizations which are opposed the activities of the I.T.A. This opposition has been declared from the early establishment of the I.T.A.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://irantkd.ir/History%20of%20org/03/03.htm|title=کانون تکواندو ایران - بخش نامه ها علیه کانون تکواندوکاران ایران|publisher=Irantkd.ir|accessdate=4 January 2015}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.irantkd.ir/_En/HisOfOrg_En.htm|title=Iran Taekwondo Association - History of I.T.A|publisher=Irantkd.ir|accessdate=4 January 2015}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://irantkd.ir/History%20of%20org/02/81-11-10.jpg|format=JPG|title=History document photograph|publisher=Irantkd.ir|accessdate=4 January 2015}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://irantkd.ir/History%20of%20org/Poladgar.jpg|format=JPG|title=History : Poladgar photograph|publisher=Irantkd.ir|accessdate=4 January 2015}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/persian/sport/story/2008/07/080727_pm-kickboxing.shtml|title=ورزش - قهرمانی کیک بوکسینگ زیر سوال|publisher=Bbc.co.uk|accessdate=4 January 2015}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|author=pr |url=http://www.worldtaekwondofederation.net/the-rise-and-rise-of-a-taekwondo-power/ |title=The Rise And Rise Of A Taekwondo Power |publisher=World Taekwondo Federation |date=2015-12-03 |accessdate=2016-04-01}}</ref>
