'''Knattspyrnufélag Garðabæjar''', abbreviated as '''KFG''', is an [[Iceland]]ic [[football club]] based in [[Garðabær]]. It was founded in 2008. The club plays in [[4.deild karla|3.deild karla]].

Notable former players:
[[Ellert Sigurþórsson]]
[[Sindri Rósenkranz]] (currently focusing on his promising darts career)
[[Andri Valur Ívarsson]]
[[Brynjar Björn Gunnarsson]]

